  "texts": [
    "The Italian high school system, \"scuola superiore,\" spans 5 years and includes lyceums, technical institutes, and professional institutes.",
    "Lyceums prepare students for university, technical institutes offer career-oriented education, and professional institutes provide vocational training.",
    "We partnered with a technical institute, working with 4 classes, all of whom were taught English by the same teacher.",
    "Two classes were in the 3rd year (median student age 16) and two in the 5th year (median age 18).",
    "All students were on the tourism track, focusing on business administration and foreign languages."
  ],
